<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>LionGateOS Travels â€” Home</title>
<link rel="stylesheet" href="theme.css">
<style>
/* :root variables moved to theme.css */
*{box-sizing:border-box}
body{
  margin:0;
  font-family:system-ui,-apple-system,Segoe UI,Roboto,sans-serif;
  background:var(--bg-dark);
  color:var(--text-main);
  display:flex;
  flex-direction:column;
  min-height:100vh;
}
body::before{
  content:"";
  position:fixed;
  inset:0;
  z-index:-2;
  /* background handled in theme.css */
}
header{
  background:var(--bg-mid);
  padding:1.5rem 1rem;
  border-bottom:1px solid var(--accent);
}
.header-inner{
  max-width:1200px;
  margin:0 auto;
  display:flex;
  flex-direction:column;
  align-items:center;
}
.brand img{
  height:120px;
  width:auto;
}
nav{
  display:flex;
  gap:2rem;
  justify-content:center;
  flex-wrap:wrap;
}
nav a{
  color:var(--text-main);
  text-decoration:none;
  font-size:1rem;
}
nav a:hover{opacity:0.9}
main{
  flex:1;
  width:100%;
  display:flex;
  flex-direction:column;
  align-items:center;
  padding:1.5rem;
}
.section{
  width:90%;
  max-width:1100px;
  background:var(--card-bg);
  padding:2rem;
  margin:1.5rem 0;
  border-radius:var(--radius);
  box-shadow:var(--card-shadow);
  text-align:center;
}
.card-link{
  display:inline-block;
  padding:0.6rem 0.9rem;
  border-radius:10px;
  background:rgba(123,108,255,0.1);
  margin:0.5rem 0;
}
.card-link a{
  color:var(--accent);
  text-decoration:none;
  font-weight:500;
}
.card-link a:hover{text-decoration:underline}
footer{
  text-align:center;
  padding:1.5rem 1rem 2.5rem;
  border-top:1px solid var(--accent);
  color:var(--text-muted);
}
</style>
</head>
<body>
<header>
  <div class="header-inner">
    <div class="brand">
      <img src="assets/logo.png" alt="LionGateOS Travels">
    </div>
    <nav>
      <a href="index.html">Home</a>
      <a href="destinations.html">Destinations</a>
      <a href="how-it-works.html">How It Works</a>
      <a href="about.html">About</a>
      <a href="disclosures.html">Disclosures</a>
    </nav>
  </div>
</header>
<main>
  <section class="section">
    <h1>Welcome to LionGateOS Travels</h1>
    <p>Your travel planning platform. Navigate the guides and resources to plan your trips efficiently.</p>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <h2>Start Here</h2>
    <div class="card-link"><a href="start_here.html">Begin with the correct order to plan</a></div>
    <p>Quick access to foundational guides for first-time and returning travelers.</p>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <h2>Explore</h2>
    <div class="card-link"><a href="destinations.html">Browse Destinations</a></div>
    <p>Learn about destination guides, environmental considerations, and travel intelligence resources.</p>
  </section>
</main>
<footer>
  LionGateOS Travels is a planning-first travel experience. Booking is completed on third-party platforms.
</footer>
</body>
</html>
